boozy ' os and the cristal gem ( also known as the cristal gem ) ( french : boozy ' os et la gemme de cristal , also known as la gemme de cristal ) is a 2013 french animation short film based on the french animated television series boozy ' os , and directed , written , scored by and starring its creator ken arsyn . it was produced by creasyn studio . the film was first released at annecy international animated film festival on april 14 , 2013 . it was presented during the dailymotion , cartoon network studios and annecy international event " + de courts ! online animation film contest by annecy " , and arrived first . the film title refers to the annecy award internationally named " cristal d'annecy " .